data.description: Looking for a gorgeous, pre-inspected, 4+ bedroom walkout? From stainless steel kitchen appliances, new lighting, and second story laundry, you'll love all the updates in this charming open-concept 2-story. The finished basement includes a rec room, non-conforming bedroom, and 3/4 bath perfect for entertaining, a remote work space, or separate living space. Enjoy stunning sunsets in the large, fully fenced west-facing yard. Perfect for kids and pets alike! Located near restaurants and shopping in the heart of NW Omaha, you just can't beat the location! Don't wait, schedule your showing today! AMA
